---
title: Spiced Cauliflower Mac and Cheese with Spinach and Crunchy Breadcrumb Topping
description: Mac and cheese could not be a more perfect comfort food.  We've jazzed it up with cauliflower and Turkish seasoning to add new dimension to a favourite and have you begging for more.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-cauliflower-mac-and-cheese-9a887925.jpg
